<h2>Create new certificate</h2><hr>
<form action="/certificates" method="post">
	<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Certifcate name:"><br>
	Select the tests that the certificate requires: <br>
	<% @tests.each do |t| %>
		<input type="checkbox" value="<%=t.id%>" name=test_ids[]><%=t.name%><br>
	<% end %>
	Creating a new certificate will automatically create equipment by the same name, if it doesn't already exist. <br> This can be edited on the equipment page.
	<input type="submit" id="create_button" value="Create certificate">
</form>